Package: ordbetareg
Type: Package
Title: Ordered Beta Regression Models With brms
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Robert Kubinec <rmk7@nyu.edu>
Maintainer: Robert Kubinec <rmk7@nyu.edu>
Description: This package implements ordered beta regression models using brms as a backend. 
   These models are for modeling continuous variables with upper and lower bounds, such as
   VAS scales, dose-response relationships and indexes. Hierarchical, dynamic and multivariate
   specifications also implemented via brms.
